data.description: A true hidden gem waiting to be discovered! Nestled in the heart of beautiful Bradenton, this home which is situated on a triple lot offers the perfect canvas for your vision. Whether you're looking for yourself, a multi-generational home, or space to run your business, the possibilities are endless with having no HOA. The 4th bedroom has a separate entrance and could be ideal for an in-law suite, home office, or business use. Step into your tropical backyard retreat complete with lush palms, your own private pool, newer shed to store your belongings, and a huge backyard with ample space for your RV or boat, complete with convenient sewer and electric hookups. There is also plenty of room to build a large garage with space to store all your toys! The kitchen is updated with modern appliances and granite countertops. Rest easy in the spacious bedrooms with plush carpets and generous closets, and unwind on one of the two lanais as you watch the Florida sunsets paint the sky. This home sits just minutes away from the gorgeous beaches of Anna Maria Island, lively downtown Bradenton, shopping, dining, and more! Don't miss the opportunity to live the ultimate Florida dream!
